      "description": "List pending invitations for the authenticated central user email.\n\n**Auth:** requires authenticated central session/token (`auth:central-api`).\n\n**Query params (strict):**\n- `filter[search]`: nullable|string|max:255\n\n**Prohibited params:** `q`, `sort`, `include`, `page`, `per_page`\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Returns only pending invitations addressed to current user email\n- Expired invitations are marked and excluded from results"
